itunes:summary:
This is something that you need to try! Japanese Psychology! I hope you can sit down and do this with me. 
Here are the questions:

Write ten things you did this past week?

What do you love?
What does the world need?
What are you good at?
What can you get paid for?

And the last three:
What have I received from?
What have I given to?
What troubles and difficulties have I caused?
